A New Mobility Scooter &ldquo;I am writing to thank you for the £1000 cheque towards the mobility scooter, which I recevied yesterday. My scooter is arriving on Friday. Your kindness will give me back my independence and enable me to get out more. I want to thank you all, without the scooter I would be very limited to what I can do.&rdquo;
Mr D, Kidderminster.
A New Bath &ldquo;Thank you for the money for myself and my children, which will be a big help for having a new bath, so that my disabled son can use it safely.
